\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c2114a262b5bd2f2b5aa9c4c4d056d995c8790","tid":1199903,"uid":3112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"振奮人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好佩服個被告肯拎條偷拍片出黎<br />\n我諗事主以為被告會驚再比人告就唔敢拎條片出黎做證供"},{"pid":"72c3154912f3e58b80107389f40bbc97ee4ac35e","tid":1199903,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e03e889cf1da3683f3d412543dc846ff27221e","tid":1199903,"uid":140606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"但唔係話女方果刻唔願意都算係非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話結左婚女方果刻唔願意都計老強<br />\n有無人可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"當事人（女方）品格有問題 / 證供不可信"},{"pid":"825e2c0fd3ccd3e8c85d2a5e8750fe0560d8aa15","tid":1199903,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e03e889cf1da3683f3d412543dc846ff27221e","tid":1199903,"uid":140606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"但唔係話女方果刻唔願意都算係非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話結左婚女方果刻唔願意都計老強<br />\n有無人可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"當時條片無顯示到女方有不願意既行為<br />\n亦同時令到女方既證供同人格變得不可信 後者已經對件案同原被告有好大影響<br />\n講真好彩佢有片 亦顯出年中辦公室 朋友間非禮亦未必全部係真 可能一切都係女方自己講"},{"pid":"2b44ed6083517a27b049bb592abd935d2186aa14","tid":1199903,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c2114a262b5bd2f2b5aa9c4c4d056d995c8790","tid":1199903,"uid":3112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"振奮人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好佩服個被告肯拎條偷拍片出黎<br />\n我諗事主以為被告會驚再比人告就唔敢拎條片出黎做證供"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:00.000Z","msg":"射落海都唔益佢 呢單唔出片就衰硬 出片衰偷拍就仲有得打"},{"pid":"d9f6200cb91e575493e499d82fa190a8c1bc7bf6","tid":1199903,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"METOO#"},{"pid":"34ae5464e37a364f86215647659afd890a011d0d","tid":1199903,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70de49e880c0b0b85d58338f7f13060c4caa42a5","tid":1199903,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"記住拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae42cd3786c685fcc1a740d484f6e0b80320a02","tid":1199903,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"淫賤醫院"},{"pid":"9537c2af96f32a358c0cd0f48f7912d3d06d5032","tid":1199903,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"僅眨眼38 次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被告好慘， 無lala 俾人告搞到要拎片出黎<br />\n雖然偷拍就唔岩， 但唔偷拍今日又證明唔到自己清白<br />\n<br />\n其實依家d 女成日拎完著數又亂尻咁告， 係咪應該告返佢地老妨呀？"}]}